見鬼講鬼話反tpp，日本同新加坡繼續FF敗登會入tpp：敗登都冇講過會話入番tpp）同俄佬（唔理俄羅斯侵略格魯吉亞同唔理侵略烏克蘭，薯仔同奧巴馬瀨因為德法唔做嘢之後所以美國自己就唔想做嘢）都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4d458266821a9418e533ef2f8dd0f4ebd9a396","tid":2383324,"uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T00:43:28.000Z","msg":"雜種稱讚拜登抗疫表現「幹得好」 敗登同雜種同意地球上只有新世界肺炎，反對歧視中共同歧視中國人<br />\n<br />\n白登簽行政命令禁官員使用「中国病毒」一詞 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2382366/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2382366/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"43d7ab4c23be56ae0957b3dcd676bbef95c569ab","tid":2383324,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T00:44:56.000Z","msg":"戰略性耐性？"},{"pid":"09183ecb9d8cd2ac8011808898a5963e8c56f44e","tid":2383324,"uid":100986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"43d7ab4c23be56ae0957b3dcd676bbef95c569ab","tid":2383324,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T00:44:56.000Z","msg":"戰略性耐性？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:12:25.000Z","msg":"黑馬、4年希拉莉+4年克里（克里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）、拜登同賀錦麗年代<br />\n<br />\n歐盟同北約:<br />\n連美國自己都唔做嘢，點解美國要我哋做<br />\n<br />\n黑馬、敗登同黑婆:<br />\n歐盟同北約做嘢會冇美國咁敏感，因為美國下下都做嘢會激嬲對家"},{"pid":"dcacb0a9e09b71b725d338ad97d009b5bc6ba3e7","tid":2383324,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:20:18.000Z","msg":"美國 俄佬 中國十足十舊時三國時代咁<br />\n平時蜀吳聯盟抗魏<br />\n樊城之戰就魏吳聯盟打蜀<br />\n孔明上台就蜀吳又friend番"},{"pid":"e0b148519d8282dc946cbfff35acc5ab6e1615dd","tid":2383324,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:41:26.000Z","msg":"e.g.<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬同拜登選嗰陣承諾:<br />\n美國會退出中東戰爭，將中東外判俾盟友（以色列、土耳其同沙特）打理<br />\n<br />\n真係選上做總統（2012年奧巴馬連埋任同敗登做美國總統）之後<br />\n（總統位已袋，話之你死）<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬同敗登:<br />\n美國某程度上要留守中東，美國唔可以就咁退出中東並將中東外判俾以色列、土耳其同沙特，對抗敘利亞獨裁總統巴沙爾（2013年伊朗、俄佬同巴沙爾用生化武器屠殺敘利亞自由軍，普京恐嚇奧巴馬同敗登唔可以出兵推翻巴沙爾之後，奧巴馬同敗登之後條底線就越隊越縮：縮到由得敘利亞自由軍俾俄佬同伊朗+巴沙爾sm）；Trump勾結俄羅斯同勾結普京可恥!<br />\n<br />\n以色列應該要同巴勒斯坦和平共處（搞到奧巴馬同副總統登任內得罪埋以色列）"},{"pid":"7857da60a250a30fa421e29d8f6f0f2cf8a4fcb0","tid":2383324,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:45:12.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎呢？"},{"pid":"5f51b764834fddd7bc105b6fa3217886b51cda8a","tid":2383324,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"207562a02112535a3697d6f569e7a2b5eae3a12a","tid":2383324,"uid":100986,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ab19e55a4efd34495b30f194f783de468291c72f","tid":2383324,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T23:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T23:39:47.000Z","msg":"敗登承諾會對俄佬更強硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"咁嚟緊俄羅斯就會靠近中國多啲,搞亂世界秩序."},{"pid":"b42812e40f50f2e53a36e40d31da1c874518c2b9","tid":2383324,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:52:46.000Z","msg":"普丁(Putin)"},{"pid":"80a516244c066789e2599345175d4bc7962a75e6","tid":2383324,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"582094900b28af3537accc9e575de9281630102c","tid":2383324,"uid":94480,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T00:00:31.000Z","msg":"普京回應：試過俄羅斯幼幼未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e94f742bedce7d8b7ee0a01bb7930cd9a1298a","tid":2383324,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f51b764834fddd7bc105b6fa3217886b51cda8a","tid":2383324,"uid":143241,"like